Dialogs.Dialog: Ah... I found this. I picked up a wallet.
Okay, I'll help you find the owner
Want to find the owner together？ Does it have a name somewhere？
Oh, lemme see... Just the initials...
We have to find the owner. For the time being, let's go to the staff room and ask around.
I see, that seems like a hard task.
You're right... I will deliver it to the staff room.
I think that's the right move.
It seems the owner of this wallet is someone from my class.
Really？ I'm glad we could find the owner.
That's right, it's all because you picked it up, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
No, it's because you helped me...
...I couldn't find the owner of the wallet.
Don't worry... I delivered it to the staff room, so I'm sure they'll find the owner soon.
Ah！ I think it's good to wash the cleaning tools sometimes, so I tried to move it, but it's heavy.
Are you sure？... Then, I wonder if tomorrow is a good day to start. Can I ask you to come tomorrow？
But I think it's better if it's clean...
(I promised to help ▲高嶺＊＊▲ clean up today.)
Yup. Let the heavy lifting to me.
Huh, that's the cleaning tool case...
It's fine, I managed to carry it by myself. Don't worry.
Excuse me... Can you bring me your survey for improving club activities？ I was asked by the sensei to collect them...
I'll fill it and bring it back
Is it okay if I skip it？
I'm sorry, I'll fill it now. Wait a little more, please.
Really？ Okay, I'll meet you again.
Can I skip it？ I don't think everyone has to do it.
I see... Yes, it's not something mandatory.
(What should I do about the survey ▲高嶺＊＊▲ asked me about？)
(▲高嶺＊＊▲ told me about the survey, but I haven't written it yet...)
Thank you for your survey, I'll submit to the sensei.
Yes, I'll leave it to you.
I hope your improvement plan is adopted.
Huh... What happened with the survey？
Ah, I'm sorry！ I couldn't write anything after all.
▲高嶺＊＊▲？ You're staring at your phone, what's wrong？
Ah... Huh, I want to send a photo with an email, but I don't know how to do it...
I know a little about it, can you show it to me？
...Yes. If you send it as it is, it's okay.
Thank you. It's amazing how you can do it even if you don't own it.
Well, every phone is similar, so no big deal.
Is that so？ Hmm... Can I ask you about it next time？
You should read the manual, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. Maybe that way you can really understand it, right？
It's not that difficult, so it's okay.
(That's right, ▲高嶺＊＊▲ said she would like to learn how to use her phone. I'll go see her.)
(▲高嶺＊＊▲, I wonder if she learned how to use her phone. I should ask her.)
I'm sorry for bothering you... Thank you for teaching me.
I feel I'm somehow better at using mobile phones.
Ah, I'm sorry. Teaching me how to use a mobile phone is a hassle, I know.
Emm... sorry. Somehow, our timings did not match.
No, it's fine. I know I'm not good using phones.
Well... I thought I'd keep cleaning the equipment after practice.
It seems difficult, do you best
You don't you have to do it alone. I'll help you.
I don't know if I'll be of any help, but I'm from the same club. Let me help you.
Thank you. I think it will take some time, but... I think we'll be okay.
That seems to be somewhat difficult, do your best.
No, I like doing this... Don't worry.
(Speaking of which, ▲高嶺＊＊▲ told me about the equipment maintenance last time...)
(Today I have to help ▲高嶺＊＊▲ do equipment maintenance...)
Thank you. With this I think it's the end.
Good work to you too. Thank you for helping me. I ended faster than I expected.
Huh... I've finished clearing the equipment. It's alright now.
Oh, I see... I'm sorry, I didn't help much.
Don't worry. I intended to do it alone since the beginning.
Hmm, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？ Do you have any problem？
Sensei sent me to collect a print, but I can't find it.
Then, why don't we look for it together？
Leave it to me. I'll go look around the school.
You're right... But I'll try to find it.
(The print ▲高嶺＊＊▲ told me about... Where I can find it...)
Is this the print you're looking for？
I'm glad. Be careful not to drop it anymore.
Yes. Hmm, thank you very much.
The print I was looking for...
Ah, that's right... I'm sorry, what happened？
I see... I'm sorry I didn't help you.
Umm, my new shoes don't fit me too well... If you'd like, could you be in the rally for a while？
I'm ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s opponent in the rally...
I can't do it... I'm sorry.
It's better to rely on good people.
(By the way, I was going to practice today with ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
Thank you, it seems that I have gotten used to my shoes.
(▲高嶺＊＊▲ seems to have more energy to spare...)
Huh, my opponent for the rally...
I'm sorry, I couldn't deal with the pressure...
It's okay, I can do it alone sometimes.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, haven't you been getting late to your home recently？
Emm, I had an errand to do after classes... my way back home was a little frightening.
I see, I'll escort you back home. Unless it's annoying for you.
That's not it... Are you sure you want to help me？
Okay... Then, thank you for helping me.
I see... Be careful if you're staying that late.
(By the way, I promised ▲高嶺＊＊▲ to help her...)
Thank you for taking your time to help me. You saved me.
No, I'm able to feel relieved each day.
Then it was worth to help you. I'm glad.
Excuse me, you promised to help me... Can you do it？
It can wait until later, right？ Sorry...
▲高嶺＊＊▲, is that a practice menu for our juniors？
I was asked to do it this time. I'm currently thinking about things to do.
I can help you with anything, just tell me.
Is there anything I can do？ Make copies or something.
Well then... It would be nice if we could try the menu together.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, I think you can assemble a good training menu.
If you say it like that...
Do your best for our juniors.
(By the way, I promised to help ▲高嶺＊＊▲ to try the menu she created...)
(I'm going to go practice with ▲高嶺＊＊▲ today...)
How did hard did you feel the practice menu for our juniors？
I think the balance is better because of the improvements you did.
Really？ I'm glad. Then, we should go with this.
No, it's thanks to you that I could improve it. Thank you.
You're welcome. It was good training for me too.
About the practice menu for our juniors...
Ah... I'm sorry, I couldn't help you.
...I'll be fine, I'll try again next time.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, what's wrong？ It looks like you're worried about something.
Oh... I'm thinking of giving a gift to Papa, but it's hard to think about something for men.
I hope you can find something
Well then, I'll give you some advice. I think I can help you.
Is that okay？ That's a big help...
Don't worry about it, I'll show you a good store.
I hope you can find a good gift for your dad.
I hope he's happy with his gift.
(By the way, I promised ▲高嶺＊＊▲ I would give her some advice on her present for her father.)
(Today I promised to help ▲高嶺＊＊▲ decide for a gift... I wonder what would be good.)
Papa was very pleased with his gift.
It was thanks to your advice. Thank you.
Umm, the gift for Papa... I ended up asking Mama.
It was Papa's favorite thing... I should have talked to Mama from the beginning...
Did you change your racket, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
No, it seems to have been replaced. The girls' club knows nothing about it, so I wonder if the boys know...
Then I'll ask in the men's club.
I know how to talk to them, leave it to me.
Right, if you ask everyone in there, you will get it back.
(That's right, I have to ask around for ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s racket location...)
(I should look around for ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s racket...)
Thank you for finding my racket. The one who took it, returned it to me.
Yes, it was in the men's club after all. I'm glad to hear it.
Yes... Thank you for listening to me.
It's not a big deal, you're welcome.
Did you find something about my racket？
It's okay... It's mine, so I'll ask myself.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, aren't you getting early to school lately？ Are you on duty？
That's right. I'm on duty to water the garden pots...
It's hard to get up early
Then... Can I go with you during your turn？
Sometimes I want to get up early, and feel like an honor student.
That's your reason？ Then... Are you sure？
Getting up early to water the plants... Sounds tough.
Not much, I think it's better to do it before everyone gets to school.
(By the way, I promised to go to school with ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
(I need to go to school with ▲高嶺＊＊▲ today...)
We've been going out at early morning, how do you feel？
I'm getting used to it. It feels good to get up early.
Hehe, right？ But today my duty is over.
It was fun because we went to school together. Thank you.
I guess it was hard to get up early.
I was on duty after all.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, what are you doing so late？
Emm... I was practicing to improve my form.
Um, if you'd like... Can I meet you here tomorrow？
I'll do it if you don't mind, but I think you should ask a more advanced person.
No, I don't believe you're inexperienced.
Well then, I look forward to it.
It's important to improve on your form, but... I can't do it.
It's not that a big deal, but... Yes, I understand.
You should ask a more advanced person.
(I was supposed to meet with ▲高嶺＊＊▲ today...)
Go to the club room first
Thank you for helping me to improve my form.
Yes, I think I'm getting better. All thanks to your help.
I hope you see the results of it in a match.
My form isn't getting any better...
I'm sorry I couldn't live up to your expectations.
It's okay, because I was just thinking sweet things.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, you've been particularly keen on practice lately, right？
Yes, I like to train in the park at night to get it right, but I was told I shouldn't go alone...
Want me to go with you？ That way you won't be alone.
That's fine, but... I wonder what I should tell Papa...
Isn't it okay to tell him "I'm going with a friend"？
Well, it's decided. Let's work together.
(By the way, I promised to go practice with ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
(I'm going to help ▲高嶺＊＊▲ practice today.)
Thank you for taking the time to help me practice. I was able to train as much as I wanted, and it was fun.
It was fun indeed... And you were amazing, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
It was thanks to you I could have fun. I don't think I could have done this alone.
It is, thank you very much.
It seems the training wasn't as effective as I expected.
No, it's because I couldn't do it properly.
Umm, I'm thinking of making homemade sweets for my friend's birthday.
If you'd like, can you taste the prototype？
Well then, are you sure you want me to try？
Far from that, I feel lucky.
Is that so？ Since it's a prototype, it may be a failure...
Hehe, it's okay, I don't make things that can't be eaten. Then, I'm counting on you.
Oh, I don't want to force you to do it... I'm sorry.
I'm sorry, I don't think I can help you.
(I promised to try some of ▲高嶺＊＊▲'s sweets today...)
How about this one？ Is it good？
Yes, this finished product will be popular even if it's put out in a store！
Really？ Thank you for your advice.
It's was all in your arms, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Thank you. Will you eat some more if I make sweets next time？
No, it's alright, I'll do my best next time.
(▲高嶺＊＊▲... How should I approach you？)
(Maybe if I'll call her differently this time. By her last name, first name, or a suffix...)
Are you alone？ If you'd like, can I tag along...？
Huh... I'm in a hurry... Sorry.
(I was refused, but it's okay to call her this way.)
(It failed... I wonder how should I call her.)
Hey, if you'd like, let's go together.
(I think it's okay to call her like this.)
(Wait, am I getting a little too friendly？)
(I think it's okay to call her like this.)
I'm glad I found you, let's go together.
(I think it's okay to call her like this.)
Whassup, why don't we go back together？
(I think it's okay to call her like this.)
I'm sorry for surprising you... Were you looking for something？
It was something I had to do...
I was looking for you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
I was just trying to call out an acquaintance...
Ah... I'm sorry, I didn't mean to disturb you... See you.
Don't worry about it. See you.
I was just trying to speak with someone...
...I'm getting in the way then. I'm sorry, I'll go now...
Actually, I was looking for you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Did you now？ What do you need of me？
Thank you. You saved me because I didn't pay attention to the sensei.
Are you okay now？ Well then, I'll help you.
Me？ But... Am I in the way？ Let me move then.
I see... I'm sorry. See you.
(Should I try to talk to her？)
Huh？ I'm sorry... Did I surprise you？
No, it was just that I...
Actually, I was looking for you ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
I have to meet with someone...
I see... Sorry for bothering you. See you.
I was thinking of calling out a friend...
I see, that was it... I'm sorry, see you.
You are the one I was looking for, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
I have a problem; I don't know the schedule for club activities.
Ah, I'll gladly help. Feel free to ask me again, okay？ See you.
Huh？ If you call people so loudly, you will bother someone, okay？ See you...
Is that so？ Sorry for calling you out.
(▲小早川＊▲ doesn't seem to be here anymore...)
(▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ doesn't seem to be here anymore...)
(I wonder if she'll be surprised when I call her out.)
You know, there was something I had to do...
Actually, I was looking for you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Ah, you know... I have something to do, then...
I understand. Well then, I'll leave you be. Sorry for bothering you.
I was looking for someone I have business with. It's not a big deal, though.
Oh, I see... I'm sorry, I'll leave you so you can find whoever you're looking for.
Sure... But, you don't have to apologize...
Actually, I was looking for you ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Ah, you saved me, that was a big help. I knew it, it was best to ask you about it ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Feel free to ask me anytime if you have any problem. See you later then.
(I don't think ▲高嶺＊＊▲ is there, anymore...)
Huh, is that ▲高嶺＊＊▲ over there？
Well... Until next time, okay？ I'm sorry.
I remembered I had something to do. I'll be going now then.
I see... Okay, I'll see you around, right？
(I can't see ▲小早川＊▲ around here anymore.)
(I can't see ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ around here anymore.)
(Huh, haven't she seen me？ I should approach her.)
Nothing. I just have a little free time and nothing to do...
There was something I had to do, but...
Ah！ Actually I was looking for you ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
I was looking for someone, and I thought I saw them over there...
Ah, sorry！ I won't disturb you, then.
...I was looking for someone, and I was trying to call them.
I... Was I in your way？ Okay, I'll see you later. I'm so sorry...
Don't need to apologize for that. See you！
I was looking for you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. I think it's a coincidence I managed to find you.
I see, so that was it. It was so easy. Thank you for helping me.
You're welcome. I'll be going now, okay？
(I'm not waiting around, I better go.)
Whassup, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. Hey, I was wondering...
...Am I on your way？ ...Um, okay... See you later.
(In the way？ Did you misunderstood me？)
Ah, you know, I'm in a hurry right now, so...
Huh, are you in a hurry？ I'm sorry, I didn't notice. I'll see you later then.
Sure, I'm sorry for that. See you.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, I'm so sorry. Are you injured？
Don't worry, I'm okay. I'm going to be late, so I'll be going now, alright？
Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！ I'm sorry, are you okay？
I'm fine, thank you. Um... And you？
Me？ I'm fine, I was the one who crashed with you.
I'm glad. I'll be late, so I'm going now, okay？
Yes, I have to hurry too！ See you.
▲高嶺＊＊▲！？ Are you okay？ Sorry for crashing with you, but I have to hurry.
Ah, sorry！ Are you okay？ Are you injured？
Yes... I'm okay, don't worry. But, I'm going now, I'm in a hurry.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, did you get hurt？ Are you okay？
Huh？ Ah, yes. Don't worry, I'm fine... I'll have to go now.
(Okay, now what was my next class...)
Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！ Hey, do you know what classes are next？
Yes, I was about to take my next class here, and...
Ah, you don't say！ I thought we had this class together today.
Hehe. This class is a different one. Okay, see you later.
Ah, I see. It was a coincidence because this class changed classrooms recently.
Really？ I wish we had a class together.
Ah... Well, I think it would be fun... I have to go now.
Ah, I understand. Then I'll let you go before you're late for your class.
Don't worry about it. I'll see you later.
(▲高嶺＊＊▲... Her skin is really beautiful...)
Ah, don't let your guard down, or you'll be late for class.
That's true, I'll see you later then.
Oh, then I have to go！ If I'm late I'll be in trouble！
Ah... I have to go too. Let's do our best！
(Mmm, now where did that thing go...？)
Hey, what's wrong？ Did you lost something？
Yes, I think it was something like this...
Be more mindful of your things, okay？ See you.
Yes. I'm sorry for the trouble.
Oh, thank you very much for picking it up.
I happened to find it because you were running around.
You saved me, I owe you.
No, it's no biggie... Ah, but is it okay if you don't hurry？ I'll be going ahead.
That's right, you saved me again！ See you！
Thank you for picking it up！ I have to hurry now before I'm late.
(So pretty... Wait！ Don't look at her eyes...)
Thank you for picking it up. You saved me.
I happened to be passing by. Don't worry. Well then, I'll be going now.
Okay. You really helped me, I owe you one.
Ah, you picked it up, thank you so much.
You're welcome. Please be more careful with your things.
(Huh？ It seems like ▲高嶺＊＊▲ is over there. Perhaps...)
Huh？ Yes, it's me. Why are you so surprised？
Well, there was a person over there, who looked like you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲... That's why.
Hehe, that's a funny mistake. See you later.
(Ah I really thought it was her...)
▲高嶺＊＊▲？ Weren't you over there just now？
Right now？ You're saying strange things, Hehe.
I see, it was my mistake. I thought she was similar to you.
Really？ I see, I guess it was a mistake after all... I'll be going now, see ya.
Oh, I was surprised because there was someone over there who looked like you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Ah, sorry about that. I thought I saw someone who was similar to you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Is that so？ Oh, I have to go now.
Well, I was sure I just saw you over there, ▲高嶺＊＊▲, so I was surprised.
Me？ I'm sure it was a mistake... Well, see you later.
Even if you look at me like that, I...
Er, well... I think you're getting a little too close.
Mmm, well... You don't have to get that close, you know...
Is there something on my face？
If you stare at me that much... Hmm...
You're staring at me too much... What's wrong？
You don't have to get that close...
Emm... Aren't you getting to close to me？
Are you taking your distance from me on purpose？
I wonder what I should do in this situation...
(I was getting too close to her, but I wasn't thinking much about it.)
(Isn't this nice？ I really feel like it is.)
Yes. But if is you, it's not as surprising.
You can count on me too... Ah, it's nothing.
I can count on you after all.
There's nothing you can do if you fail.
If you care too much about it, it's not good.
I think it's better for you not to get depressed.
I can't do anything about it...
Er, well, how are you doing？
Can't do anything about it now.
Don't worry about it every time it happens. Just, don't change your mind, okay？
...I think we should go with what you're thinking.
Hey, what will you do now？
I see... Hey, what are you doing？
Oh I see. Hey, what are you doing？
Well, if it's you... Then, yes.
I wonder if you'll be able to see such a wonderful place...
That's right, that was your election.
I see... I won't take it then.
What is it...？ Ah, it's nothing, don't worry.
Just a little more... Hmm, it's a pity.
How is the job in the library committee？ Is it worthwhile？
It's worth doing it... I wonder if that's sounds right, I don't know how to say it...
However, it's a good thing that the number of books borrowed increased because of the committee members.
Are the committee members good friends？
Only a handful get along. And the rest only do chat between themselves.
So that was the case, after all...
Umm... I have something to ask you.
You're doing part-time job, right？ It seems hard, but I think it's worthwhile.
Well, you're right... It can be painful and troublesome, but there are also fun things.
Well, I think it's more like being friends in a part-time job, rather than being a customer.
I want to hear more about it.
Huh, ▲高嶺＊＊▲, are you interested in part-time jobs？
I knew it, after all, aren't there many girls also doing part-time jobs lately？
And that means making friends with other girls.
How are you doing in your classes？ I wonder if you're getting along with your classmates.
I wonder 'bout that... I think we are getting pretty good.
Even though you transferred recently, it's an amazing thing.
No, I think it's amazing. If it was me...
(▲高嶺＊＊▲, you make a cute face when laughing.)
I know you live alone. How difficult has been for you？
Yeah, it's amazing. You're a high school student living alone. I wonder how your every day is...
I know！ If you're that interested, want to come and see？
No... it's just... that's a little...
Geez, don't make fun of me...
Well, hmm... I don't mind it, if you don't want to answer...
You have a good friend from the first year on the library committee, right？
And you have a senpai at your part-time job...
I see... And you are friends with them...
What's wrong with that？ Is that bad？
No... it's alright, I think you should have as many friends as possible.
Huh？ Well, yeah. I think so.
I might not be on good terms with them but, I want to be on better terms with you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Ah, you're right. That's good. Yes, I want to get along with you too...
You see... I've heard some strange rumors, so do you mind if I ask you some questions？
I asked the library committee, and they said you get along with a first-year.
At you part-time job... I've heard you get along with a senpai from school.
I knew it... Are you really getting along with them？
No. Even if you care about it, there's nothing you can do.
I'm sorry. I was just a little worried. That's it.
Well, you might have heard things like that. The truth is, I speak with you more often, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Is that so？ Yes, thank you.
Well, you know... I have something to ask you.
Is there a first year student in the library committee you're getting along with？
And you're getting along with the senpai at you part-time job, right？
I knew it. Do you really get along so well？
You don't try to hide it...
Wha-？ Well yes, I mean... Why？
I get along with you too, you know.
(▲高嶺＊＊▲, I wonder what's on your mind？)
So it was just a rumor.
I mean, I speak with you more, right ▲高嶺＊＊▲？ Even now, don't we？
Hehe, I see. Let's get along even more, okay？
Emm, that's... Yes, I was just trying saying "Whassup"...
That's right... Trying is important！ I'm kidding.
Why do you stay with me？
It's just that... I don't think there's nothing interesting about me.
Well, I don't think that's true... It think it has to be with the fact...
It's because you're here, with me. We're together because it's fun.
(▲高嶺＊＊▲, I'm hearing you say some weird things lately...)
I was recently wondering if I have changed.
Hmmー, now that you mention it, I do wonder about it...
Yeah, it's true, you've become brighter than before.
Yes, I really feel like you shine more than before.
(I wonder where you heard that, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
(It's a sports equipment store... I wonder if there's something we could use for our activities.)
I don't think it's a coincidence, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Two tennis club members meet at a equipment store. Do you think it's a coincidence？
So, we could meet because we have a purpose...
Yes, it's inevitable！ Maybe it's fate！
Well, now that you say it, you might be right...
Well, I was just making things up. I was just hanging around.
Huh？ Ah... Geez, don't tease me.
▲高嶺＊＊▲ you're always so serious. Let me know if you know about some good equipment.
Sure, as a serious tennis member I will tell you. Hehe.
I often use that kind of thing...
Thank you, I learned something new today.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, you seem to be very good at teaching people.
I wonder about that... I don't know.
That's how it started with Yumi-chan... I'm not that good nor confident.
Mmm. That's how it began. I wasn't confident I was doing the right thing...
How can I know if I'm doing the right thing？
Hmmー I wonder. I don't think many students know the answer... ▲高嶺＊＊▲, isn't your father a good teacher？
Papa？ Yeah... That's a good idea, I will try to ask him.
Thank you for the advise. If Papa teaches me, I might become a spartan... Hehe.
(Spartan...？ ▲高嶺＊＊▲ is seriously going to ask her father.)
(Ah, there are some cooking utensils over here...)
(I think it might be a good idea to cook for myself... Hmm.)
Oh, what a coincidence. Are you doing some shopping？
That's right. I've come to buy ingredients to make sweets.
